title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 325-3.6 - License to cover only employer's employees
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 325-3.6 - License to cover only employer's employees

State Regulations

No license shall be issued to an employer to cover any
but his own employees except as indicated in section
325-3.5
of this

Subpart. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
§§
325-3.6

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
